  "title": "Business Development Executive (Digital marketing) HSW",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Effectively communicate with clients to understand their digital marketing needs and offer solutions to their problems</li><li>Develop and present proposals customized for each client’s digital marketing needs</li><li>Prepare and deliver pitches and presentations to prospective clients</li><li>Handle objections and negotiate with prospective clients</li><li>Ensure excellent customer relationships through regular follow-up and building rapport with key decision makers</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Excellent communication skills</li><li>Min 1 year experience in Digital marketing and 1 year experience in sales / business development</li><li>Able to work independently to achieve targets</li><li>Consultative sales ability</li><li>Knowledge and experience in SEO, GEO, SEM and Social Media Marketing is advantageous</li></ul><p><br /><strong>HOW TO APPLY:</strong></p><p>Interested applicants, kindly send your resume in MS WORD format or please click on “Apply Now”.</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website</p><p>www.trustrecruit.com.sg.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Hong Sze Wai (Sharon)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R25128240</p>",
